.TH CORTEX-PLAN 1 "2026-03-23" "cortex-plan 2.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
cortex-plan \- Command-line tool
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cortex-plan
[
B-h
    R | 
        B--help
               R]
.br
.B cortex-plan

ICOMMAND
        R [
           ISUBCOMMAND
                      R] [
                          IARGS
                               R...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cortex-plan
.SH COMMANDS
Available commands:
.TP
.B list
List all plan files
.TP
.B view
View a plan file
.TP
.B edit
Edit a plan file in $EDITOR
.TP
.B path
Show the plans directory path
.TP
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show help message and exit
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT
Override for context directory (set automatically by Claude Code when running plugin commands)
.SH FILES
.TP
.B ~/.claude/
Default context directory containing agents, modes, rules, and other configuration
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR cortex-plan-tui (1),
.BR cortex-plan-workflow (1)
